      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"embrace the darkness\" bit is kinda heavy. but like, what do you actually mean by that? if nothing matters and it's all just a temporary accident, isn't the most logical \"embrace\" just to stop playing the game? like, why keep the struggle going at all if the end result is always just zero?",
